{"tid":2319173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[大清算］Facebook被控違反反壟斷法　或被迫出售WhatsApp及Instagram","createTime":"2020-12-10T02:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T03:18:36.000Z","uid":92125,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0a750203c00e2cc4b75ed503d6626d2729e1e459","tid":2319173,"uid":92125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:08:18.000Z","msg":"Facebook（美：FB）被控違反反壟斷法，有可能會被迫出售WhatsApp及Instagram。Facebook股價昨夜收報277.92美元，跌1.93%。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦貿易委員會（FTC）及48個州份對Facebook提出反壟斷訴訟。Facebook被指在 2012年收購社交媒體Instagram， 以及2014年收購即時通訊軟件WhatsApp，以建立一個反競爭的社交網絡環境，認為這兩宗交易理應被取消。<br />\n<br />\n紐約總檢察長Letitia James表示，近10年來Facebook利用其市場主導地位及壟斷力量壓制較小規模的競爭對手，強調要恢復巿場信心， 必須對付任何扼殺競爭， 傷害小企業及減少創新的行為。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook總法律顧問Jennifer Newstead回應指，反壟斷法不是要用來懲罰成功的公司，在Facebook投資數十億美元來開發應用程式後，WhatsApp及Instagram有更好的發展，消費者可以從免費提供的WhatsApp服務中受惠。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook是全球最大社交媒體， 用戶多達27億， 巿值接近8000億美元。"},{"pid":"f91c7118cba38758f5a8d81529876c33bcd6484e","tid":2319173,"uid":16811,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:10:30.000Z","msg":"比source 啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2691656be04d0f03102bf0bb34532b193ea739","tid":2319173,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:11:39.000Z","msg":"會比騰訊買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd849a8bde3847275a1baadd6c68041e03ba502c","tid":2319173,"uid":92125,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f91c7118cba38758f5a8d81529876c33bcd6484e","tid":2319173,"uid":16811,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:10:30.000Z","msg":"比source 啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"Hket 唔post link啦"},{"pid":"68973777093fd9d166764ed0859033b9b3372dff","tid":2319173,"uid":126198,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd849a8bde3847275a1baadd6